6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower">Summoner</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.midnightfury.org">Armies</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->!</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shilochveneficus>Shiloch Veneficus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#333333>(3/7/03 1:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1880.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: CotAM</span><hr size=1> Most charms with the exception of a couple are random duration. CHA and the mob's resists are just ways to help you land the spell (keep the mob from resisting it). So, you need CHA and resist debuffs to land it, but after the spell lands, its some random number that was rolled up at the time it took hold, which is no longer than the max duration listed on Lucy. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140815> Master Shiloch Venzolmes</a> - Arch Convoker - Walkers</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thoorne>thoorne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#333333>(3/7/03 1:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1880.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://metacarpes.free.fr/images/thoornehead.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: CotAM</span><hr size=1> Well. The CHA/Debuff thingie is total bullshit.<br>
<br>
After 2 weeks of soloing in BoT, I tested all combinations possible with high CHA, with Malosinia in, or without both.<br>
<br>
Result is... That it's nearly the same. Many people say that debuff and cha have importance. But it's total BS sorry.<br>
<br>
Just charm the mob, and go fight. The -100 MR on spellcast is far enough to never get resisted. (I got 0 resist since I do solo). <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=156959">Thoorne Darkmagi</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
